window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The five members of an elite commando group nicknamed \"the Stone Wolves\" once raged against Creterakian rule. Now, four decades after their heyday, they each try to stay alive and eke out a living. But a friend from the past won't let them move on, and neither will their bitterest enemy.&nbsp;Hopscotch, RedWire, the Killer, Lulz, and Recoil will soon wish their pasts could stay dead.</p>"; 
